name: MGET
description: MGE (Metaverse Golden Empire) is a project jointly launched by Singapore HJW FOUNDATION LTD and Germany's blackamoor blockchain laboratory. Token: 'Metaverse Golden Empire token' is issued on BSC, abbreviated as: MGET, the total circulation is: 10 billion, the main token is mined by the game. Metaverse Golden Empire is a blockchain simulation economic game that truly belongs to players. It is a deep integration of NFT and is open to all players. Players can earn MGET (Metaverse Golden Empire token) through mining.
